  <CalDefinition Description="his calibration informs the tuner whether a mast antenna is included as part of the Infotainment configuration.   Only configurations with the mast antenna option are required to run the Antenna Mast Installation Verification test. If True, includes mast antenna. If false, doesn't include mast antenna. Default is False." Name="AntennaConfiguration" References="GIS-653-7200" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
