  <CalDefinition Description="This calibration sets the signal threshold for determining the presence of an AM strong station during an Update Station list sequence.  The value of this calibration may or may not be the same as the cal used for AM strong station thresholds used during normal tuning operations.  This provides more flexibility for tailoring the test criteria independently of the strong station threshold used in the production calibration." Name="AM_AntMastSignalThreshold" References="GIS-653-7200" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
